{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"5fa94c13-9902-4b30-9dda-6a65458e2853","agentId":"acd42c3c17b035e39","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Visually inspect these slides for user-visible defects.\n\nLook for:\n- Overlapping elements (text through shapes, lines through words, stacked elements)\n- Text overflow or cut off at edges/box boundaries\n- Decorative lines positioned for single-line text but title wrapped to two lines\n- Source citations or footers colliding with content above\n- Elements too close (< 0.3\" gaps) or cards/sections nearly touching\n- Uneven gaps (large empty area in one place, cramped in another)\n- Insufficient margin from slide edges (< 0.5\")\n- Columns or similar elements not aligned consistently\n- Low-contrast text (e.g., light gray text on cream-colored background)\n- Low-contrast icons (e.g., dark icons on dark backgrounds without a contrasting circle)\n- Text boxes too narrow causing excessive wrapping\n- Leftover placeholder content\n\nFor each slide, list user-visible issues. Skip sub-pixel positioning and cosmetic nitpicks a viewer wouldn't notice.\n\nRead and analyze these images:\n1. /tmp/slide-01.jpg — Cover (META wordmark, 3 stat callouts BULLISH/+34.5%/3:1)\n2. /tmp/slide-02.jpg — Headline thesis (3 KPI cards, navy callout strip at bottom)\n3. /tmp/slide-03.jpg — Four data sources (2x2 grid)\n4. /tmp/slide-04.jpg — Four-lens framework (2x2 grid with verdict pills)\n5. /tmp/slide-05.jpg — Lens 1 Fundamentals (column chart left, 4 stat cards right)\n6. /tmp/slide-06.jpg — Lens 2 Technicals (6 red bullet signals left, mint counter-evidence card right)\n7. /tmp/slide-07.jpg — Lens 3 Options (2x2 stat cards left, line chart right)\n8. /tmp/slide-08.jpg — Lens 4 Valuation (horizontal bar chart left, $820 callout card right)\n9. /tmp/slide-09.jpg — Synthesis (verdict matrix table + navy callout)\n10. /tmp/slide-10.jpg — Trade plan (3 tranche cards + stop / target row)\n11. /tmp/slide-11.jpg — Disclaimer / closing (dark navy)\n\nOutput: per-slide list of any user-visible defects, then a final summary \"OK to ship / fixes needed\"."},"uuid":"b31d049b-6791-428d-a552-aa0adbe76b83","timestamp":"2026-05-09T18:43:30.643Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"local-agent","cwd":"/Users/rahul/Library/Application Support/Claude/local-agent-mode-sessions/5138ffb4-3739-4715-99b8-0e15e83d49f7/b1776684-e921-4dde-bb66-147c0bba8c5b/local_1fc68325-6434-4789-be93-30b31351f94d/outputs","sessionId":"6b93a8da-37ba-4999-8497-c41695ea6766","version":"2.1.121","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
